Harry Hays Morgan Jr. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Hays_Morgan_Jr. 0 Harry Hays Morgan Jr. (April 25, 1898 – July 8, 1983) was a Swiss-born American diplomat, society figure and actor. He is most notable as the brother of Gloria Morgan Vanderbilt and uncle of Gloria Vanderbilt.
